Package: ItemRest
Title: Automated Item Removal Strategies in Explatory Factor Analysis
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Ahmet", "Çalışkan", , "ahmet-caliskan@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for identifying and testing low-quality items in exploratory factor analysis (EFA)
    using automated strategies, including cross-loading and low-loading criteria. Generates summaries
    for each removal strategy based on explained variance, factor loadings, and internal consistency.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
